Class DefaultSwingRenderer

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.elvenrings.qdemo.view.AbstractRenderer
      • com.elvenrings.qdemo.view.swing.DefaultSwingRenderer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    SwingRenderer
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    FillBlankSwingRenderer, MultipleChoiceSwingRenderer, SingleChoiceSwingRenderer

    public abstract class DefaultSwingRenderer
extends AbstractRenderer
implements SwingRenderer
    An abstract class that provides the following functionality
    1. Ability to register/de-register listeners.
    2. Rendering of the Preamble and Body parts of a Question on a QPanel.
    Since:
    1.0
    Author:
    Iliasu Salifu, iliasu@elvenrings.com
